    Car Detection

    Install package

    To use the geoai-py package, ensure it is installed in your environment. Uncomment the command below if needed.

    In[1]:
    Copied! 
    # %pip install geoai-py
    # %pip install geoai-py

    Import libraries

    In[2]:
    Copied! 
    import geoai
    import geoai

    masks_path="cars_masks.tif",
    output_path="cars.geojson",
    mask_threshold=127,

    erode_kernel_size=3,
    erode_iterations=1,
    use_watershed=True,
)
